casebody.data:
Jeremy Marquise CARTER, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
MIAMI-DADE CIRCUIT COURT, et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1945 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 03, 2018 EMAS, LUCK and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Petitioner is deemed insolvent and may proceed in forma pauperis for purposes of this cause.

Following review of the petition for writ of mandamus, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
